    "description": "Parents of school-age children face the same chaotic morning ritual every day but have no tool that specifically helps anchor it — generic task apps don't understand \"school starts at 8:45 and we need to leave by 8:20.\" EarlyRise is a family morning routine app with countdown-aware task sequencing: set your leave time, add each child's morning steps with time estimates, and the app works backwards to tell you right now if you're on track or running late. Visual, calm, and designed to be the single screen on the kitchen counter every school morning.",
    "ideaNumber": 4,
